"sont bienvenus."
msgstr ""
"I initially developed blunderDB for my personal use to help detect "
"patterns in my mistakes. However, it's very rewarding to receive "
"feedback, especially after spending a lot of time on design, coding, and "
"debugging. So feel free to reach out to share your experiences. All "
"(constructive) feedback is welcome."

